technologicalApplicability.value:
Sandwich panel made of a PIR foam component expanded without the use of CFCs and HCFCs. Coated on both sides with embossed centesimal aluminium. Ideal for the thermal insulation of industrial roofs, walls and floors. Thanks to its lightness and great rigidity, it is easy to move and position during installation.
 "PIR polyisocyanurate sandwich panels with centesimal aluminum coating:
- UNIKO.22 AL (thicknesses 60mm, 80mm, 100mm, 120mm)
- ISO TT Centesimal aluminum (thickness 60mm, 80mm, 100mm, 120mm)
It is specified that “UNIKO.22 Al” and “ISO TT Alluminio centesimale” are two commercial names that identify the same product."
